item.title: My Week in Music #3: 2018/10/19 - 2018/10/26
item.description: Last.fm is a website that can keep track of users and their listening habits. I’ve been listening to music with Last.fm since 2010 and am slightly obsessive over my music stats. These stats are for my listening from the past week. My week for October 19, 2018 to October 26, 2018 Top 10 Artists Top 10 Artists Coheed and Cambria (-) Even though I’ve been making a conscious decision to not listen to as much Coheed and Cambria, I’m still listening to them quite a lot.
